items.section_excerpt: If you want to witness the ancient hand weaving process and buy handicrafts of Aurangabad then you've got to visit the Himroo Factory for this unique and authentic experience in Aurangabad. You can also buy some textiles like Paithani sarees, handloom shawls, furnishings, bed covers, cloaks and coats.
